  "text": "## 6. STANDING ORDERS & DIRECT DEBITS  \n### 6.1 Standing Orders  \nA standing order is a regular, fixed transfer you set up.  \n**Setup:**\n- Specify payee, amount, frequency (weekly/monthly/etc.)\n- Provide receiving account details\n- Standing order executes on scheduled date  \n**Cancellation:**\n- Cancel at any time (no notice period required)\n- Cancellation effective immediately\n- Future payments blocked",
